Dr Gardner Murray, Australian Chief Veterinary Officer, asked me to post the
following update to OIE on events relating to the current outbreak of
Newcastle disease in New South Wales, Australia.
--
Dr M.J. Nunn
Acting Director
Animal and Plant Health Branch
Bureau of Resource Sciences
